listing.description: This beautifully designed newly constructed "detached" home sits behind the gated community of Terrassa and is distinctively positioned on a premier lot. This sophisticated home is nearly 2500 square feet with 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms plus a generously sized play room/media area. Upon entrance, you are captivated by the real wood floors and high ceilings that invite in the natural light. The gourmet kitchen is emphasized by stainless steel appliances, an over-sized center island and granite counter tops which opens to the informal dining area and great room, that create a broad living space accentuated by large windows. The elegant master suite offers a grand walk-in closet, exquisite master bathroom with dual vanity sinks and a separate walk-in shower/tub. The low maintenance back yard allows for privacy with plenty of space to entertain. Additional features include; a main floor bedroom, recessed lighting, nicely sized 2 car garage with direct access, inside laundry room with an abundance of space and custom flooring throughout the entire home. This Terrassa community offers pool/jacuzzi, playground, and BBQ area.
